-What?

287
00:27:27,687 --> 00:27:29,189
I'm so sorry, sir.

288
00:27:29,272 --> 00:27:32,359
-He's drunk.
-Why are you apologizing, bitch?

289
00:27:32,442 --> 00:27:34,152
-I asked you a question.
-Stop!

290
00:27:34,235 --> 00:27:36,738
-What are you doing?
-Sir! You can't do that!

291
00:27:36,821 --> 00:27:38,490
