306
00:28:30,625 --> 00:28:31,793
Yeah, all right.

307
00:28:33,712 --> 00:28:37,298
And we'll go this way. To B1.

308
00:28:38,341 --> 00:28:39,426
Sound good?

309
00:28:40,677 --> 00:28:41,803
Uh, yeah.

310
00:28:57,444 --> 00:28:59,654
